-- Turkey's Garanti bank to secure $500 million of financing 
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Fri Jul 25, 2014 02:35AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 25 (Reuters) - Turkey's Garanti Bank <GARAN.IS> said on Friday it mandated its headquarters to secure $500 million of financing with a maturity of maximum 5 years.

